project_descr: The main objective of the project is to capacitate Bureaus of Finance and Economic Development, Woreda Finance and Economic Offices and Sector Bureaus and empower them for effective delivery of UN assisted programmes and projects.

outputs.output_descr: The project primarily intends to augment the implementation capacities of BoFEDs and sector bureaus so that they will be able to implement development projects and programs effectively in their respective regions by embedding qualified human resources

project_title: capacity development offinancebureaus and sector bureaus
